# nginx-proxy-template
This repository contains a template to create a NGINX image


# Commands

Running locally
```
docker run -d -p 80:80 -p 4200:4200 --name nginx nginx:latest
```

Connect to the Docker image and run bash
```
docker exec -it nginx bash
```

Build image
```
docker build . -t "nginx-proxy-template:1.0.0"
```

Run image
```
docker run -p 80:80 -p 443:443 -d  --name nginx nginx-proxy-template:1.0.0
```


Shorthand
```
docker stop nginx && docker rm nginx && docker build . -t "nginx-proxy-template:1.0.0" && docker run -p 80:80 -p 443:443 -d  --name nginx nginx-proxy-template:1.0.0
```